# Backend Dashboard Policy (API/WebSocket only)

- Do NOT add or re-enable server-rendered dashboard routes.
- Allowed:
  - WebSocket endpoints under `/api/dashboard/ws/*` → [app/api/dashboard_websockets.py](mdc:app/api/dashboard_websockets.py)
  - Compatibility REST data under `/dashboard/api/*` → [app/api/dashboard_compat.py](mdc:app/api/dashboard_compat.py)
- Disallowed:
  - New Jinja templates or HTML views under `/dashboard` (legacy is deprecated)

Main app wiring: [app/main.py](mdc:app/main.py)
Legacy template retained only with deprecation notice: [app/dashboard/templates/dashboard.html](mdc:app/dashboard/templates/dashboard.html)
